{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had-- and he suffered a sepsis from an operation in April of 1937, which was a-- probably a fortunate, in a sense, that he was spared the persecution, especially in the terrible disappointment that-- because he had thought that this persecution would never happen, would never, never take place.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then to realize, so-- 1938, a year later when this all happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he, he died in the-- in the-- not knowing what, what terrible things would happen after had he lived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kristallnacht, I was in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- [DRINKS] I was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I, I didn't see-- I wasn't, you know-- that's happened during the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, I didn't see that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not-- I was too young to be allowed-- to go outside-- to go out at night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we saw the damage the next day and, of course, heard it on the radio--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I just saw some broken windows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't see anybody being, you know, mistreated or, you know, or beaten, I didn't see that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean-- and they don't really-- played that down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't-- they didn't-- the Nazi propaganda machine wouldn't say, we beat them and tortured or we-- or we-- and even killed somebody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just said, these people are responsible for all the bad things that have happened in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're just paying them back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we're destroying their stores and synagogues, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't really talk about that they killed anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "See, they never-- that's why-- talk about the concentration camps, was-- you know about what was going on in concentration camps, really, they played that down.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
